        <abstract> 
<p>Much amused at the <hi rend="italic">Witness</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Pleased at what THH says on hybridity.</p>
            <p>Odd that objectors never allude to the arguments that alone have weight in their favour – affinities, rudimentary organs, etc.</p>
            <p>Has 16 ill in the house!</p> 
<p><hi rend="italic">Natural History Review</hi> a capital number.</p> 
